{"tid":1456272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果機場要走既 可以去貨運區避    比多條路大家選擇","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:05:48.000Z","uid":190705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b564dded3236fb7453e1d910164ca669dd5b8e98","tid":1456272,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/175426_d109f41693de28b65c653189d43afc16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F175426_d109f41693de28b65c653189d43afc16.jpg&h=ce5204c2&s={SIZE}\" />   <br />\n真係走唔到就行過去貨運區 <br />\n幾個巴士站<br />\n再唔係入HATCL/AAT避 <br />\n果邊好多空運司機交貨<br />\n同樣地好多貨<br />\n班狗未必夠膽開火(催淚彈果類) 入面好多DG貨<br />\n<br />\n利申 空運行業.  另做過AVSECO(機場保安班撚樣)"},{"pid":"12c4245a8e26a5c3ee1146b6c9e39cc096a28c5b","tid":1456272,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d51f2a68155938886876ea9ec7e9b7bb4ef3f5b","tid":1456272,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"因應機場的交通情況，龍運以下路線會因應實際情況作出改道安排，乘客請依照在場外勤人員指示。<br />\n<br />\n各A線巴士不停「一號客運大樓站」及「二號客運大樓站」，以機場巴士總站為終點站<br />\n<br />\nA31, A36, A41, A33X<br />\n直接前往港珠澳大樓旅檢大樓站，以機場巴士總站為終點站<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n另外，現時安排E線以國泰城為循環點返回新界各區。"},{"pid":"50800334423b1693126bcaef6a60b4185a78e68e","tid":1456272,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd10a68b46955d461f1d0f30c1a2d9727b20ae28","tid":1456272,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c4245a8e26a5c3ee1146b6c9e39cc096a28c5b","tid":1456272,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"咪膠啦....我盡幫手足都係想."},{"pid":"70a1bbaa77622840a0ec7483fd2289b3c2f47b70","tid":14562